        </item>
        <item>
            <title>打機都可以聞到現場味道   GameScent 可放出模擬煙硝、泥濘、賽車場燒胎等 6 種氣味</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/03/gamescent/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=gamescent</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/03/gamescent/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 08:30:47 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[GameScent]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1222051</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">遊戲界日新月異，經常性會有新產品推出，增加玩家遊戲體驗。最新推出的 GameScent 可發出模擬火藥等 6 種味道，令玩家更能置身於遊戲世界中。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Discover the future of entertainment right here —&gt; <a href="https://t.co/hz9LpiyECC">https://t.co/hz9LpiyECC</a><a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/gamescent?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#gamescent</a><a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/gamescentrevolution?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#gamescentrevolution</a><a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/gaming?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#gaming</a><a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/smellreality?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#smellreality</a><a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/ai?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#ai</a><a href="https://t.co/qpINfQzAYu">pic.twitter.com/qpINfQzAYu</a></p><p>&mdash; Gamescent (@GameScentAi) <a href="https://twitter.com/GameScentAi/status/1761820742256361811?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">February 25, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p style="font-weight: 400;">GameScent 現時可發出 6 種氣味，包括火藥槍火煙硝味、爆炸燃燒味、森林自然空氣、大雨風暴泥濘味、賽車場的柏油與燒胎味，以及中和以上味道的空氣清新劑，並使用了 AI 辨識遊戲環境而發出相應氣味。GameScent 適用於主機、PC、VR 等裝置，未來亦會新增更多氣味，例如割草、血跡等。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">GameScent 除了會發出氣味之外，還有空氣淨化功能。GameScent 現已開賣，售價為 179.99 美元（約 1,408.96 <span data-mid="/m/02nb4kq" data-name="港元">港</span>元）。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_55992"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/BA8jKdpPLCo?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://gamescent.com/">GameScent</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/03/gamescent/game-channel/">打機都可以聞到現場味道   GameScent 可放出模擬煙硝、泥濘、賽車場燒胎等 6 種氣味</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
